Commentary Text: Ravi Bishnoi to Morgan, out Russell Run Out!! Russell's probably gone here. A direct hit from short third man. Actually no, Rahul has stuck a glove out and deflected the throw onto the stumps. Russell's well short anyway. It was his call to charge across after Morgan edged a googly.
